### Aurelia API — Phase 5 incidents

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@incidentTypeId = replace-with-incident-type-id
@incidentLevelId = replace-with-incident-level-id
@incidentId = replace-with-incident-id
@immediateActionId = replace-with-immediate-action-id
@investigationId = replace-with-investigation-id
@actionPlanId = replace-with-action-plan-id
@evidenceId = replace-with-evidence-id

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Catalogs
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List incident types
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/types

### List incident levels
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/levels

### Dashboard summary
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/dashboard/summary

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Incidents
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create incident
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "incidentTypeId": "{{incidentTypeId}}",
  "incidentLevelId": "{{incidentLevelId}}",
  "title": "Derrame menor en área de prueba",
  "description": "Registro de prueba para validar el flujo de incidentes fase 5B.",
  "occurredAt": "2026-06-24T01:00:00.000Z",
  "immediateResponseSummary": "Se aisló el área y se contuvo el evento.",
  "environmentalImpactSummary": "Sin impacto ambiental observable al momento del reporte."
}

### List incidents
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents

### List incidents by status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents?status=reported

### Get incident detail
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}

### Update incident
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Derrame menor en área de prueba actualizado",
  "environmentalImpactSummary": "Evento controlado y sin impacto ambiental observable."
}

### Update incident status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "under_review",
  "comment": "Pasa a revisión ambiental."
}

### Close incident
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/close
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "comment": "Incidente cerrado luego de completar acciones y validación."
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Flash Report
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create or update flash report
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/flash-report
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "summary": "Flash Report de prueba para incidente ambiental controlado.",
  "immediateCauses": "Falla operacional durante una maniobra de prueba.",
  "affectedComponents": "Área operacional de prueba.",
  "potentialImpact": "Potencial afectación localizada si no se contenía oportunamente.",
  "reporterName": "Usuario de prueba"
}

### Get flash report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/flash-report

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Immediate actions
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List immediate actions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/immediate-actions

### Create immediate action
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/immediate-actions
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Aislar el área y contener el derrame.",
  "status": "completed",
  "performedAt": "2026-06-24T01:20:00.000Z"
}

### Update immediate action
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/immediate-actions/{{immediateActionId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed"
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Investigations
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List investigations
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/investigations

### Create investigation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/investigations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "method": "five_why",
  "title": "Investigación causa raíz derrame menor",
  "summary": "Investigación inicial para identificar causa raíz."
}

### Update investigation
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/investigations/{{investigationId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "summary": "Investigación completada con causa raíz documentada.",
  "completedAt": "2026-06-24T03:00:00.000Z"
}

### Upsert five why analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/investigations/{{investigationId}}/five-why
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "problemStatement": "Se observó material fuera de contención primaria.",
  "why1": "Porque una maniobra generó pérdida de contención.",
  "why2": "Porque el acople no quedó completamente asegurado.",
  "why3": "Porque no se verificó el cierre antes de iniciar la maniobra.",
  "why4": "Porque el checklist operativo no exigía esa confirmación.",
  "why5": "Porque el procedimiento no estaba actualizado.",
  "rootCause": "Procedimiento incompleto para verificación de acoples."
}

### Upsert PEEPO analysis
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/investigations/{{investigationId}}/peepo
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "people": "Operador sin recordatorio formal del paso crítico.",
  "environment": "Área operativa con condiciones normales.",
  "equipment": "Acople sin daño visible.",
  "procedures": "Procedimiento requiere actualización.",
  "organization": "Falta reforzar verificación previa a maniobra."
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Action plans
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### List action plans
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/action-plans

### Create action plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/action-plans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "investigationId": "{{investigationId}}",
  "title": "Actualizar procedimiento de maniobra",
  "description": "Agregar verificación explícita de acoples antes de iniciar la maniobra.",
  "dueAt": "2026-07-01T12:00:00.000Z"
}

### Update action plan
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/action-plans/{{actionPlanId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "completed",
  "completedAt": "2026-06-25T12:00:00.000Z"
}

# ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Evidences, comments and export
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create evidence for incident
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/evidences
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Evidencia incidente prueba",
  "description": "Evidencia creada para vincular a un incidente.",
  "evidenceType": "photo",
  "capturedAt": "2026-06-24T01:30:00.000Z"
}

### Link evidence to incident
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/evidences/{{evidenceId}}/link
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "relationType": "incident_evidence"
}

### List incident evidences
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/evidences

### Create incident comment
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/comments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "body": "Comentario de seguimiento del incidente.",
  "isInternal": false
}

### List incident comments
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/comments

### Export incident payload
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/export

### Export incident PDF base
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/incidents/{{incidentId}}/export/pdf
